This tutorial will guide you through the deployment of Iperf client and server in two different  Docker  containers.  This tutorial is different since you don't have to create a VNFPackage but you need to build two Docker images.  Create a file called Dockerfile for the Iperf client image that looks like:  FROM networkstatic/iperf3

ENTRYPOINT  iperf3 -c $SERVER_HOSTNAME -t 300  and then you can build it as:  docker build -t iperfclient .  Do the same for the Iperf server:  FROM networkstatic/iperf3

EXPOSE 5201

